---
const appUrl = 'https://app.dwellhub.in';
const desktopScreenshot = '/app-showcase/desktop-dashboard.png';
const mobileScreenshot = '/app-showcase/mobile-dashboard.png';
---

<section class="relative px-8 py-20 lg:py-28 max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
  <div class="lg:col-span-6 z-10">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-on-tertiary-container bg-tertiary-container/10 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 font-label">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">verified</span>
      30-Day Free Trial For New Societies
    </span>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tight leading-[1.08] mb-4 font-headline">
      Apartment &amp; society management, <span class="text-on-tertiary-container italic">built to feel premium.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-label font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-8 max-w-md">Society Management Software for Apartments, Villas &amp; Gated Communities in India</p>

    <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed font-body">
      Dwell Hub gives your committee one polished operating system for billing, collections, complaints, approvals, residents, and gate activity. Start with a 30-day free trial for up to 50 flats, unlock every core workflow from day one, and move to premium at ₹20/flat/month when you are ready.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-2xl px-6 py-5 min-w-[13rem] editorial-shadow border border-primary/20">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-on-primary/70 font-label mb-2">Free Trial</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-on-primary font-headline">30 Days Free</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-on-primary-container font-body">All core features included for up to 50 flats. No card. No onboarding fee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-2xl px-6 py-5 min-w-[13rem] editorial-shadow border border-primary/5">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface-variant font-label mb-2">Premium</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary font-headline">₹20/flat/month</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">Transparent pricing after trial. 50 flats = ₹1,000/month with no module add-ons.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href={`${appUrl}/register`} class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity editorial-shadow">
        Start 30-Day Free Trial
      </a>
      <a href="#mobile-apps" class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold tracking-wide hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        View App Screens
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-emerald-600">check_circle</span>Live on desktop, Android, and iPhone</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-emerald-600">check_circle</span>Billing, complaints, visitors, reports</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lg:col-span-6 relative flex items-center justify-center lg:self-center">
    <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-4 w-56 h-56 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto sm:pb-24">
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-primary/10 bg-surface-container-lowest p-4 editorial-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-3 pb-3">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary font-headline">Operations, billing, and resident overview</p>
          </div>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary">Admin Dashboard</span>
        </div>
        <img src={desktopScreenshot} alt="Dwell Hub desktop dashboard showing billing, complaints, and resident activity" class="w-full rounded-[1.5rem] border border-primary/10 object-cover" loading="eager" />
      </div>

      <div class="hidden sm:block sm:absolute sm:-bottom-10 sm:right-0 sm:w-52 rounded-[2rem] border border-primary/10 bg-surface-container-lowest p-2 editorial-shadow">
        <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-primary/10 bg-surface overflow-hidden">
          <img src={mobileScreenshot} alt="Dwell Hub mobile app showing society overview and payments" class="w-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
